reviewText:
Excellent dvd collection.  Too bad it is only region 2.
I found a region free set by searching buysellcommunity.com or ioffer.com.

One cannot describe Jonathan Meades TV programs; one has to experience them for ones rself.  Funny, intellectually stimulating and very entertaining, and a genuine breath of fresh air  on TV.  An acquired taste, some may say, but this is definitely one for the adventurous.
The Jonathan Meades box set is rectilinear perfection.
